{"title":"Jones Motorbikes Plus LWB HD/e is a heavy duty DIY ebike frameset","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/02/19/jones-motorbikes-plus-lwb-hd-e-is-a-heavy-duty-diy-ebike-frameset/","date":1613743223000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>Jeff Jones, maker of fully rigid off-road bicycles and components, has today announced the new Jones Plus LWB HD/e. Those acronyms stand for Long Wheel Base and Heavy Duty/ebike. Its arrival is huge news for Jones Bikes, being the debut frameset of a new Jones Motorbikes brand.&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-motorbike-bafang-ebike-motor.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-motorbike-bafang-ebike-motor.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x341/rscb8/ng:webp/ngcb8\" alt=\"jones plus lwb hd/e heavy duty ebike mtb rigid frame motorbike bafang mid drive\" width=\"1200\" height=\"846\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-motorbike-bafang-ebike-motor.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x341/rscb8/ng:webp/ngcb8\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-motorbike-bafang-ebike-motor.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-motorbike-bafang-ebike-motor-297x209.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-motorbike-bafang-ebike-motor-800x564.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-motorbike-bafang-ebike-motor-120x85.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-motorbike-bafang-ebike-motor-768x541.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-motorbike-bafang-ebike-motor-696x491.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-motorbike-bafang-ebike-motor-1068x753.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-motorbike-bafang-ebike-motor-596x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 596w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-motorbike-bafang-ebike-motor-100x70.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 100w\" ezoid=\"0.27610217563629047\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-motorbike-bafang-ebike-motor.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-motorbike-bafang-ebike-motor-297x209.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-motorbike-bafang-ebike-motor-800x564.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-motorbike-bafang-ebike-motor-120x85.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-motorbike-bafang-ebike-motor-768x541.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-motorbike-bafang-ebike-motor-696x491.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-motorbike-bafang-ebike-motor-1068x753.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-motorbike-bafang-ebike-motor-596x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 596w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-motorbike-bafang-ebike-motor-100x70.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 100w\"></a></p><p>Jones Motorbikes is home to the familiar Jones Bikes frames you’re used to, only with electric motors. Jones have taken their <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2019/07/26/jones-complete-boxed-bicycle-line-gets-longer-with-jones-plus-lwb-build/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Plus LWB</a> frame and made a few key alterations to make it stronger and stiffer to withstand the additional forces associated with ebikes.</p><h3>Jones Plus LWB HD/e</h3><p><span><iframe width=\"696\" height=\"392\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation\" data-ezsrc=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/fNUb8ltroaw?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en-US&amp;autohide=2&amp;wmode=transparent\"></iframe></span></p><p>The information in this video is everything we know about Jones Motorbikes so far. But, for those of you who don’t want to watch a 4:30 video, here’s a quick summary:</p><p>The Jones Plus LWB HD/e is <em>almost</em> the same as the original Plus long wheel base bicycle, only stronger, stiffer, a little heavier, and the chainstay is one inch longer. Why longer stays? Jones say the longer rear centre helps prevent unintentional wheelies when the motor engages, and it permits sufficient chainring clearance for compatibility with mid-drive motors such as those offered by Bafang.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-ebike-truss-fork-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"eager\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-ebike-truss-fork-1.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng%3Awebp%2Fngcb8%2Frs%3Adevice%2Frscb8-1\" alt=\"jones plus lwb hde motorbike bafang mid drive motor\" width=\"1200\" height=\"711\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-ebike-truss-fork-1.jpg 1200w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-ebike-truss-fork-1-297x176.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-ebike-truss-fork-1-800x474.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-ebike-truss-fork-1-120x71.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-ebike-truss-fork-1-768x455.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-ebike-truss-fork-1-696x412.jpg 696w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-ebike-truss-fork-1-1068x633.jpg 1068w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-ebike-truss-fork-1-709x420.jpg 709w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\"></a></p><p>The frame has a standard threaded BB with no eccentric, helping to save a little on weight and allow space enough for the installation of BB motor kits. Chainring clearance is massive allowing the fitment of up to a 50T chainring.&nbsp;</p><p>The LWB HD/e gets heat-treated chromoly tubing, only it is thicker with different butting profiles to the standard LWB to add strength and stiffness, making the frame more suitable for carrying big loads. In keeping with that intention, the bike gets a kickstand so you can prop it up fully loaded with all your bikepacking gear.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Jones-Motorbikes-Plus-LWB-HDe-ebike.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Jones-Motorbikes-Plus-LWB-HDe-ebike.jpg\" alt=\"jones motorbikes yellow plus lwb hd/e bikepacking ebike frame\" width=\"1200\" height=\"670\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Jones-Motorbikes-Plus-LWB-HDe-ebike.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Jones-Motorbikes-Plus-LWB-HDe-ebike.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Jones-Motorbikes-Plus-LWB-HDe-ebike-297x166.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Jones-Motorbikes-Plus-LWB-HDe-ebike-800x447.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Jones-Motorbikes-Plus-LWB-HDe-ebike-120x67.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Jones-Motorbikes-Plus-LWB-HDe-ebike-768x429.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Jones-Motorbikes-Plus-LWB-HDe-ebike-696x389.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Jones-Motorbikes-Plus-LWB-HDe-ebike-1068x596.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Jones-Motorbikes-Plus-LWB-HDe-ebike-752x420.jpg 752w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Jones-Motorbikes-Plus-LWB-HDe-ebike.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Jones-Motorbikes-Plus-LWB-HDe-ebike-297x166.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Jones-Motorbikes-Plus-LWB-HDe-ebike-800x447.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Jones-Motorbikes-Plus-LWB-HDe-ebike-120x67.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Jones-Motorbikes-Plus-LWB-HDe-ebike-768x429.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Jones-Motorbikes-Plus-LWB-HDe-ebike-696x389.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Jones-Motorbikes-Plus-LWB-HDe-ebike-1068x596.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Jones-Motorbikes-Plus-LWB-HDe-ebike-752x420.jpg 752w\"></a></p><p>Jeff Jones calls this a DIY ebike. That’s because you can pick up a frameset and spec it how you like, with the mid-drive motor and battery pack of your choice tailored to the power and/or range you need. It is specifically made to become an ebike.&nbsp;</p><h3>Pricing &amp; Availability</h3><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-ebike-truss-fork-loaded.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-ebike-truss-fork-loaded.jpg\" alt=\"jones plus lwb hde ebike loaded\" width=\"1200\" height=\"650\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-ebike-truss-fork-loaded.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-ebike-truss-fork-loaded.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-ebike-truss-fork-loaded-297x161.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-ebike-truss-fork-loaded-800x433.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-ebike-truss-fork-loaded-120x65.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-ebike-truss-fork-loaded-768x416.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-ebike-truss-fork-loaded-696x377.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-ebike-truss-fork-loaded-1068x580.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-ebike-truss-fork-loaded-775x420.jpg 775w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-ebike-truss-fork-loaded.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-ebike-truss-fork-loaded-297x161.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-ebike-truss-fork-loaded-800x433.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-ebike-truss-fork-loaded-120x65.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-ebike-truss-fork-loaded-768x416.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-ebike-truss-fork-loaded-696x377.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-ebike-truss-fork-loaded-1068x580.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/jones-plus-lwb-hde-ebike-truss-fork-loaded-775x420.jpg 775w\"></a></p><p>The Jones Plus LWB HD/e is available as a frameset with either a uni-crown or Truss fork (in steel or <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2019/12/17/jones-tig-up-titanium-plus-swb-spaceframe-and-diamond-frames-with-truss-fork/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">titanium</a>). It will also be available as a stock complete non-motorized bike, and as a complete ebike with a number of choices of motor size and battery pack. Hang on in there for pricing info. We’re working on it.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.jonesmotorbikes.com/?mc_cid=1753cacfb2&amp;mc_eid=a1eda91f15\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>JonesMotorbikes.com</em></a></p></div></div>","author":"Jessie-May Morgan","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"191acb3abf0742d4b726c8c3ba61df450ad0f19806a6681c1cac8ca8fcb56c10","category":"Cycling"}